&lt;p style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;The PCI Security Standards Council (PCI SSC) announced the release of its inaugural Annual Report, marking a significant milestone in the Council’s nearly 20-year history of advancing global payment security through industry collaboration, innovation, and education.&lt;/p&gt;

